# Task 2- Tic-Tac-Toe AI(Minimax Algorithm)
### Run
```bash
javac TicTacToeAI.java
java TicTacToeAI

Sample OutPut:
You are X, AI is O
   |   |  
-----
   |   |  
-----
   |   |  

Enter your move (row col 0-2): 0 0
X |   |  
-----
  | O |  
-----
  |   |  

AI plays:
X |   |  
-----
  | O |  
-----
  |   | X

Winner: O
```
# Task 4- Recommendation System
### Run
```bash
javac RecommendationSystem.java
java RecommendationSystem

Sample OutPut:
Enter a movie title: Inception
Recommended movies similar to Inception:
- Tenet
- Interstellar
- The Prestige
```


